---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { site } from '../lib/site.config';
---

<BaseLayout title={`Example Prompts — ${site.name}`} description="Copy-paste AI prompts to vibecode your customer site.">
  <Header slot="header" />

  <!-- Page header -->
  <section class="bg-primary-dark py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-accent text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.25em] mb-4">Copy & paste</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold text-white">Example prompts</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-white/55 text-lg">
        Ready-to-use prompts for Claude Code and GitHub Copilot. Just swap in your customer's details.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Prompt categories -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-background">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-16">

      <!-- Initial setup -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">🏢 Initial customer setup</h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-6">Use the built-in <code class="bg-surface px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-border text-xs">customer-setup</code> skill to configure everything at once.</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-primary-dark rounded-xl p-5">
            <pre class="text-sm text-white/80 whitespace-pre-wrap leading-relaxed"><code>Set up this template for a law firm called "Smith & Partners".
They want a professional, trustworthy feel.
Primary color: navy blue (#1B3A5C).
Accent: gold (#C9A84C).
Email: info@smithpartners.com
Location: London, UK</code></pre>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-primary-dark rounded-xl p-5">
            <pre class="text-sm text-white/80 whitespace-pre-wrap leading-relaxed"><code>Configure this for a yoga studio called "Still Point".
Calm, minimal, lots of whitespace. Muted sage green palette.
They offer classes, retreats, and teacher training.</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Design -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">🎨 Design & styling</h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-6">Use <code class="bg-surface px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-border text-xs">update-theme</code> or <code class="bg-surface px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-border text-xs">design-component</code> skills.</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-primary-dark rounded-xl p-5">
            <pre class="text-sm text-white/80 whitespace-pre-wrap leading-relaxed"><code>Update the theme to use warm earthy tones — terracotta primary (#C2703E),
cream background (#FFF8F0), and a serif display font like Playfair Display.</code></pre>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-primary-dark rounded-xl p-5">
            <pre class="text-sm text-white/80 whitespace-pre-wrap leading-relaxed"><code>Design a testimonials section with 3 client quotes in cards,
each with a star rating, client name, and company. Use a subtle
background pattern.</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pages -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">📄 Adding pages</h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-6">Use the <code class="bg-surface px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-border text-xs">add-page</code> skill.</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-primary-dark rounded-xl p-5">
            <pre class="text-sm text-white/80 whitespace-pre-wrap leading-relaxed"><code>Add a pricing page with three tiers: Starter ($29/mo),
Professional ($79/mo), and Enterprise (custom pricing).
Include a feature comparison table.</code></pre>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-primary-dark rounded-xl p-5">
            <pre class="text-sm text-white/80 whitespace-pre-wrap leading-relaxed"><code>Add a team page showing 4 team members in a grid.
Each person should have a photo placeholder, name, role,
and a short bio. Include LinkedIn links.</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-text mb-2">✍️ Content rewriting</h2>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-6">Just describe the customer and ask.</p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-primary-dark rounded-xl p-5">
            <pre class="text-sm text-white/80 whitespace-pre-wrap leading-relaxed"><code>Rewrite all page content for a craft brewery called "Hop & Grain".
Tone: friendly, passionate about craft beer, slightly playful.
Services: taproom visits, brewery tours, private events, wholesale.
Values: quality ingredients, community, sustainability.</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tip -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-surface border-t border-border">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <strong class="text-text">Pro tip:</strong> After the initial setup, iterate page by page. Ask the AI to refine one section at a time — it produces better results than trying to do everything in a single prompt.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</BaseLayout>
